"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-how-photographer-jerome-brouillet-grabbed-the-perfect-surf-shot-picture-image-see-look-gabriel-medina-breaking-viral\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9998590026955798, \"rank\": 0.00013252162161967376, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbHow photographer grabbed the perfect surf shot - PICTURE  Jerome Brouillet knew to expect fireworks when he saw Brazilian surfer Gabriel Medina paddle into one of the day's biggest waves.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9998590026955798, \"rank\": 0.00013252162161967376, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 262, \"end\": 268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerome\", \"score\": 0.9999786481581739, \"rank\": 2.135072379767508e-05, \"text\": \"Jerome\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerome\"}, {\"begin\": 269, \"end\": 278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\"}, {\"begin\": 333, \"end\": 347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Medina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AFP photographerJerome Brouilletknew to expect fireworks when he saw Brazilian Olympic surferGabriel Medinapaddle into one of the day's biggest waves at one of the world's heaviest surf breaks.\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy the Paris Olympic Games 2024 experience at your favourite ATKV Resort!\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 652, \"end\": 656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ATKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What he did not know was that his picture of Medina kicking out of the wave after a ride that earned a record Olympics score in Tahiti would become aglobal sensation, and likely a defining image of the sport and the Games.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 794, \"end\": 800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999997999112, \"rank\": 2.001383014811876e-10, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section for free-to-read content  Brouillet was on a boat in the channel - an area of deeper, calmer water to the side of the wave but without a clear line of sight of the initial action.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was exactly where he wanted to be.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brouillet was in a prime spot waiting for Medina to \\\"kick out\\\" - exit the wave face at the end of his run.\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1250, \"end\": 1256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5017399285917874e-23, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every photographer is waiting for that.\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You know Gabriel Medina, especially at Teahupo'o will kick off and do something,\\\" said Brouillet.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Medina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know something is going to happen.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The only tricky moment is where he is going to kick out?\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because I am blind!\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1572, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes he makes an acrobatic gesture and this time he did that and so I pushed the button.\\\"\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brouillet caught Medina soaring ramrod-straight above the waves pointing one finger in the sky, his surfboard pointing skyward at his side.\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think that when he was in the tube he knew that he was in one of the biggest waves of the day.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He is jumping out of the water like 'man, I think this is a 10',\\\" said Brouillet.\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1981, \"end\": 1990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brouillet suspected he had also captured something special but wasn't 100 percent sure.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I am shooting at Teahupo'o I do not shoot in such a high burst mode, because at the end of the day, if you push too hard on the button you come back with 5,000 shots in a day, and I do not like that!\\\"\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got four shots of him out of the water and one of the four shots was this photo.\\\"\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The picture has been used by scores of publications around the world and shared or liked millions of times online.\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This may well be the greatest sports photo of all time,\\\" Australian media conglomerate News.com.au posted on its Facebook page.\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TIME magazine described it as \\\"the defining image of triumph of the 2024 Summer Games\\\".\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2622, \"end\": 2635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_(magazine)\", \"score\": 0.9999999172960122, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TIME magazine\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_(magazine)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_(magazine)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medina posted the image on his own Instagram account, quickly attracting more than 2.4 million likes.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2711, \"end\": 2717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5017399285917874e-23, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 2746, \"end\": 2755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5527414174522386e-26, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the accolades, Brouillet said celebrations would have to wait because he still had the rest of the competition to shoot.\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2837, \"end\": 2846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am sleeping at a friend's house near Teahupo'o and we will have a quiet one because if tomorrow the event is on, I have to wake up at five in the morning!\\\"\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 3102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By Garr